over the AG-UI protocol at `/agui` via Agno's AgentOS. Run it with any ASGI
server, e.g. `uvicorn {{agent_module}}_serve:app`.

AgentOS mounts the `AGUI` interface; the mounted agent is built once here via the
sibling module's `build_agent` factory. Agno resumes `external_execution` gates
(the HITL write-tools) natively inside its AG-UI router — this app carries no
hand-rolled resume machinery.
"""
